<!-- TWO SERVICES -->
<section class="section section-black">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">02, Two Services We Offer</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Mechanical repair when a component fails. Vent cleaning when lint and restriction are the problem.</h2>

    <div class="services-split">
      <div class="svc-card">
        <div class="svc-badge badge-repair">🔧 Mechanical Repair</div>
        <h3>When a component has actually failed</h3>
        <p>The dryer has a broken part, heating element, thermal fuse, thermostat, drive belt, motor, drum bearing, or door switch. We diagnose, quote, and repair.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Heating element failure (electric dryers)</li>
          <li>Gas valve or igniter failure (gas dryers)</li>
