        <h3>How much does commercial dryer repair cost?</h3>
        <p>Commercial diagnostic is $120, applied to the repair or vent cleaning if approved. Most repairs run $150–$450. Heating element, thermal fuse, thermostat, or drive belt is in this range. Vent cleaning runs $120–$200 per dryer. Written estimate before any work begins.</p>
